"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"FAUNA:6.10\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">6.10</span> 標題：飛蛾（moth）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來：עָשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：‘ash)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:19\">JOB 4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:9\">JOB 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:28\">JOB 13:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:18\">JOB 27:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:12\">PSA 39:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:9\">ISA 50:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:8\">ISA 51:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:12\">HOS 5:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來：סָס</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：sas)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:8\">ISA 51:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σής</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：sēs)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:20\">MAT 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:33\">LUK 12:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis42:13\">SIR 42:13</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">討論</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p><figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0646_moth_larva.jpg\" alt=\"WEB-0646_moth_larva\"></figure>學者普遍認為，《希伯來聖經》中的<em>‘ash</em> 指的是飛蛾，<em>sas</em> 指的是飛蛾的幼蟲階段，而新約中的<em>sēs</em> 也是指飛蛾。提及飛蛾的上下文總是與破壞或損壞衣服有關，因此顯然是指一種在衣服上產卵的蛾，這就把該種飛蛾限定在谷蛾科（學名<em>Tineidae</em> ）裡的衣蛾中的一種，很可能就是網衣蛾（學名<em>Tineola biselliella</em> ）。雖然聖經將這種損害歸咎於飛蛾，但實際上是蛾的幼蟲破壞了衣物。聖經使用<em>‘ash</em> 一詞的時候，有可能是同時指蛾及其幼蟲。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p><figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0644_moth.jpg\" alt=\"WEB-0644_moth\"></figure>衣蛾是棕色或灰色的小飛蛾，會在衣服或衣料上面產卵。卵孵化成非常小的毛蟲，而且幾乎一孵化出來就立即開始吃布的纖維。毛蟲發育到一定程度後結繭，只有頭部伸出繭外，最後羽化成飛蛾。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">特殊意義或象徵意義</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>飛蛾是腐爛、荒廢和緩慢毀滅的象徵。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:19\">JOB 4:19</a> ：對於這節經文的最後一部分，大多數譯本都依照希伯來文本來翻譯，「他們像飛蛾一樣，很容易就被壓碎了。」</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:18\">JOB 27:18</a> ：對於這節經文的前半部分，大多數譯本都遵循《七十士譯本》和《敘利亞文譯本》，解作「他把房屋建造的像蜘蛛網一樣」，而不是像希伯來文所寫的：「他像蛾一樣建造房屋。」然而，如果蛾蛹也稱為<em>‘ash</em> ，那麼這段希伯來文可以解作「他把房屋建造的像蛾繭一樣」，基本上就與希臘文和敘利亞文譯本的詩歌意象相同。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:2\">JAS 5:2</a> ：這節經文使用了一個動詞，意思是「被飛蛾吃了」，其中包含<em>sēs</em> 這個名詞的衍生詞。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
